{"tid":2253875,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"PayPal 開放加密貨幣的買賣交易，甚至可以用來網購","createTime":"2020-10-22T12:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:45:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c87fd3cf82f36e5bf542c3ae5ac1f6d5db966ac4","tid":2253875,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"網路支付平台 PayPal 是很多人用來網購、轉帳的工具，但再過一陣子居然連加密貨幣也能處理了。PayPal 宣佈他們將會在美國開放加密貨幣，如比特幣的買賣，甚至能當作購物的結帳貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n在明年初開始，使用者能利用加密貨幣 PayPal 來支付全球超過 2,600 萬家商戶的帳單，不過商戶將不會從 PayPal 收到加密貨幣，而是會以法定貨幣結算，即美元、港幣等。<br />\n<br />\nPayPal 同時會提供資訊，教導使用者了解背後的區塊鍊技術、數位貨幣的生態系統，當然也有提到投資加密貨幣的風險了。PayPal 將不會收取使用者儲值加密貨幣的手續費，在今年年底前的買賣也不會產生費用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/paypal-venmo-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-ethereum-litecoin-payments-110038803.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fpaypal-venmo-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-ethereum-litecoin-payments-110038803.html&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=7107238e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/paypal-venmo-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-ethereum-litecoin-payments-110038803.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7d341221984c967f45e81aa1b558d6f76b796d3","tid":2253875,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"連登井底撚:加密貨幣只係一堆數字好唔安全"},{"pid":"16298a9f8beaf3c0c42188644a04e0399ca790ec","tid":2253875,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e3287f418f6700940006a179edf65d2eb8a5c94","tid":2253875,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港戶口幾時有"},{"pid":"f079cd70d6b2eba2a3dbe9a252b9fe80a7d2c769","tid":2253875,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"crypto係用黎交易既咩？用黎炒架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.p